data.description: Don't have to wait for Summer to visit the Lake! Discover a hidden gem nestled in the picturesque Canyon Lake Forest 2 area - a delightful open floor plan 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence that can serve as your dream home or the perfect vacation getaway. Mere three years old and gently lived in, this property exudes a sense of modernity and comfort. Step into the well-appointed kitchen and be captivated by the stunning upgraded granite countertops, adding a touch of elegance to your culinary endeavors. Both bathrooms have been lavishly adorned with the same granite, providing a consistent luxurious feel throughout. The primary suite offers a spacious haven for relaxation and a generously-sized closet for all your storage needs. Two additional bedrooms, thoughtfully placed on opposite ends of the residence, offer ample space and privacy for family or guests. Enjoy the captivating views of the surrounding natural beauty from the inviting front porch or retreat to the rear porch for a more secluded atmosphere. Seize the opportunity to own this charming property and savor a harmonious blend of modern living and nature's serenity, all in one fantastic package.
